description: Amundi MSCI USA Daily (-1x) Inverse UCITS ETF Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the MSCI USA Short Daily strategy Index ("the Index"), while minimizing the volatility of the difference between the return of the Sub-Fund and the return of the Benchmark Index (the "Tracking Error"). The expected Tracking Error under normal market conditions is 1% maximum. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi MSCI USA Daily (-1x) Inverse UCITS ETF Acc
